    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start. One thing my clients have brought up is that 'neat' can be subjective. How would you advise someone on hair styling specifically? Like, if they have very textured or unconventional hair, what's the best way for them to style it so it still looks 'polished' and doesn't distract from their authority in the boardroom?",
